overview:
Espagne immobilier is a recent website dedicated to the selling of real estate properties in the Costa Blanca, in Spain.

This website has been purposedly designed for the French Market, where hundreds of people are looking for the selling of house in Spain.

Either for vacations, secondary residence of to settle down for good, people will be able to find thousands of real estate offers in the website. They can easily browse through criteria such as the range of price, the situation and the type of house, with a private swimming pool, sea views. Thanks to that, users will be able to find the offers that meet perfectly their needs.

The website also proposes different projects and well-situated plots where houses can be built according to the client’s demands.
